br/><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; float: none; background-color: transparent;" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b3130446833526910706T9G.jpg" border="0"/><br/>&nbsp;《美国队长2》的上映，直接把电影市场带离了惨淡的3月。一周票房超过3亿人民币，全球票房也在两周内</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">突破了3亿美元。接下去，还有《超凡蜘蛛侠2》、《X战警：逆转未来》等一系列超级英雄电影虎视眈眈，</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">准备上阵掘金！<br/>随着《美国队长2》的大卖，漫威影业出品的超级英雄电影，成为史上最赚钱的系列电影。外媒有人用狄更斯</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">的名言形容说，</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; 这是“超级英雄最好的时代”。<br/>&nbsp; 漫威把以前线性发展的系列电影发展成了网状结构。每个超级英雄就像星空上的一颗小星星，他们互相辉映，</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">构成了一个宏大的世界体系。每一部新的漫威电影，都可 以看做是上一部电影的续集、番外篇，以及下一部</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">电影的预告片。从来没有一个系列电影野心大到这等程度！想想看，在未来漫威上映了近百部电影之后，这</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">个宇宙 的图景会是何等广阔和奇妙？<br/></p><p><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b4130446833529650863ENH.jpg" border="0"/><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; float: none; background-color: transparent;" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b5130446833532481025WDJ.jpg" border="0"/><br/>&nbsp; 由徐瑞宁治疗过的病人全都痊愈出院，这也使得徐瑞宁信心倍增，直至骄傲自大，这些都被徐瑞宁的大学老师方</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">教授看在眼里。方教授受到其学生的请求，让徐瑞宁诊断一位特殊的病人任小妍（莫文蔚 饰），这位病人的十分</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">怪异，她看过的心理医师没有一名能够治疗她的病情，任小妍讲话虚实难辨而且懂得如何回击治疗师。这让徐瑞宁</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对她产生了极大的兴趣……<br/></p><p><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b6130446833533281070W4F.jpg" border="0"/><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; float: none; background-color: transparent;" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b7130446833536241240ZZY.jpg" border="0"/><br/>&nbsp; 电影《同桌的你》创意来源于1994年高晓松创作的校园民谣《同桌的你》。主要讲述了周小栀和林一这一对同桌</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从初中、高中、大学直至毕业十年后的青葱记忆和甜蜜恋情。影片拍摄取景地包括北京、厦门、纽约、费城，辗转</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中美两国四地。同桌，是每个人都曾有过的同伴，他/她伴随着我们整个刻骨铭心的学生时代，我们的青春记忆里</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">他们一定是道重要的光景，而电影《同桌的你》将重现我们学生时代的熟悉片段，展现我们这一代人集体的青春</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">回忆！<br/></p><p><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b8130446833537041285LWR.jpg" border="0"/><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; float: none; background-color: transparent;" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b91304468335396714363Z2.jpg" border="0"/><br/>&nbsp; 乔伊的生命中有着三个重要的女人。第一位是道恩(薇琪·麦克卢尔饰演)，她为他生下了一个孩子，在乔伊失踪之后</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">被迫沦为黑帮大佬的性奴隶。第二个女人是伊莎贝尔(维多利亚贝维克饰演)，她也是一个无家可归的流浪者。第三</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">个女人是修女克里斯蒂娜(阿嘉塔·布泽克饰演)，乔伊在最无助的时刻遇见了她，并且渐渐爱上了她。之后乔伊意外</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地获得了一个冒充他人身份的机会，于是他义无反顾地开始了复仇以及寻求救赎的计划。<br/></p><p><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b10130446833540451481NHW.jpg" border="0"/><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img title="图片" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; float: none; background-color: transparent;" src="http://i.kesion.com/UploadFiles/2014-5/75/b11130446833543441652ISN.jpg" border="0"/><br/>&nbsp; 郑惠清（杨千嬅 饰）与丈夫邱健章（曾志伟 饰）结婚多年。但丈夫的婚外情及父母的关系疏离，令她心有郁结；</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">惠清弟弟郑伟滔（古天乐 饰）是一表人才的“补习天王”，妻子郭恩恩（梁咏琪 饰）为名模，但他却一直介怀女儿</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">外貌不美；郑东（吴孟达 饰）在发妻过身后，与夜总会工作的TA姐（吴家丽 饰）为伴，却被儿子伟滔冷眼看待，</p><p style="padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: break-all; -ms-word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">父子关系恶劣，家庭暗藏危机，各人烦恼难以释怀……<br/></p><p><br/></p>', N'<h3 class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" nmshow="_naq.push({&#39;page&#39;:&#39;1&#39;, &#39;areaId&#39;:&#39;1900020000&#39;, &#39;bucket&#39;:&#39;E1&#39;, &#39;show&#39;:&#39;buyContent&#39;})">【团购内容】</h3><p>- 电影票<span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（1张，价值110元）</span><br style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/>-&nbsp;2D通兑，观看3D影片需要补5元差价<br style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/>- 如遇国家限价片，补差金额以店内公告为准<br/><br/>- 2张糯米券可在明发二期的IMAX影城观看IMAX影片，或者VIP厅观影</p><p><br/></p>', N'<p><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(251, 252, 253);">1、有效使用日期：2014年04月29日-2014年05月31日&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2;"/><span style="color: rgb(92, 92, 92); line-height: 26px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 宋体, Verdana, STHeiTi, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(251, 252, 253);">2、使